  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to test the hypothesis that dietary n-3 PUFA will have a
      beneficial effect on systemic and local markers of inflammation when combined with
      traditional, non-surgical periodontal therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
